{"tid":2188491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【陳彥霖死因研訊】應陪審員要求再索知專閉路電視片 惟未能拍下彥霖脫鞋經過","createTime":"2020-09-04T09:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4b48db9fd6cc45c116a494569bbf125115cfe0","tid":2188491,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。死因庭今繼續研訊，庭上早前播放知專閉路電視片段，拍下彥霖曾手持疑似青協的戒大麻單張，惟下一個鏡頭卻顯示她兩手空空。陪審員欲得知彥霖「喺處於乜狀態捨棄身上所有嘢」，堅持要查看相關片段，及索閱知專閉路電視的平面圖。負責調查的警員今再度出庭，呈交相關閉路電視片段，惟未能拍下彥霖放下物品及脫鞋經過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/5HXIEXAITRCZHPHZGKKMGC3VYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2F5HXIEXAITRCZHPHZGKKMGC3VYE%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=e1b64b17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2F5HXIEXAITRCZHPHZGKKMGC3VYE%2F&h=980849d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/5HXIEXAITRCZHPHZGKKMGC3VYE/</a>"},{"pid":"438f3a57693dd74f2a15fce057ea63f5cabfba13","tid":2188491,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"未能拍下彥霖脫鞋經過 係死角影唔到定係 下一秒無左對鞋"},{"pid":"c679f496e54178dbf93e1cfebe14004c818b687a","tid":2188491,"uid":365109,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f588376277849bfef013fa608025d20fee60d94","tid":2188491,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"睇個撚樣間學校應該已經剷撚咗成條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個職訓局系統根本就係同流合污"},{"pid":"1bf80f8b0d993116c09ab012652d8deca69f7db2","tid":2188491,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c679f496e54178dbf93e1cfebe14004c818b687a","tid":2188491,"uid":365109,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"依家就係想做到所以後生都吸毒同精神病，所以先上街"},{"pid":"1a6f18d40563023f1b7021cf9b5cca0f16632119","tid":2188491,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438f3a57693dd74f2a15fce057ea63f5cabfba13","tid":2188491,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"未能拍下彥霖脫鞋經過 係死角影唔到定係 下一秒無左對鞋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"可能跟本無除過鞋<br />\n俾人捉住扔落海梗係拍唔到"},{"pid":"9e3f424759bc9add98ee17ee84c5d50d73c2ce50","tid":2188491,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">全部都無故消失 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【陳彥霖死因研訊】<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">再播片未發現彥霖物品消失經過 <br />\n周一重召化驗師</span><br />\n2020-09-04 16:19<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳彥霖死因研訊今續，共32名證人作供完畢後，研訊主任決定第3度重召負責剪輯知專設計學院閉路電視片段的警員出庭，並播放早前遺漏的片段釋慮，惟最終仍無功而返，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">相關鏡頭根本無法拍到彥霖身上物品消失經過</span></span>，僅能收窄她丟失鞋子的範圍，而<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">鞋子至今仍未尋回</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n彥霖失蹤當晚、即去年9月19日，從知專學院的閉路電視片段來看，彥霖身處李惠利大樓9樓時，頸上仍有黑色掛飾，並手持物品，仍有穿鞋。惟相隔約10分鐘後，鏡頭轉至校園內B座2樓，此時<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">彥霖身上的物品已無故消失</span></span>，陪審團遂要求法庭向知專索取該10分鐘的鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n駐守港島東區重案組的警員李豪傑表示，昨已取得4個樓層的閉路電視鏡頭分佈圖，以及共20個外置硬碟，當中包括上述遺漏之片段。李惠利8樓鏡頭顯示，此時的彥霖頸上仍纏有黑色掛飾，手持電話及傳單，腳上仍穿著鞋子。<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭轉至6樓，只見彥霖頸上掛繩疑似轉至手上，落樓梯時將其擱在地上，惟步下兩步後又回頭撿起。彥霖繼續落樓梯，走至4樓時手上黑繩仍存在，惟走至A座2樓時，已不見其手持物品。<br />\n<br />\nC座10樓的數個鏡頭顯示，起初彥霖仍有穿鞋，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">未幾鞋子已無故消失</span></span>，估計鞋子在鏡頭拍不到的小路中脫下。<br />\n<br />\n死因庭下周一會重召政府化驗所化驗師，解釋毒理測試所涵蓋的藥物，以及<span class=\"red\">陳母</span>或作結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">死因裁判官暫訂於下周五引導陪審團。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\nSource: 頭條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRFhcCj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRFhcCj.png&h=e6d9ab4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n2019 校方話 <span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">原片已遺失??<br />\nWhy???</span></span><br />\n咁警方剪輯的 cctv 來自？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39Q1Ek3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39Q1Ek3.jpg&h=e13837cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7fd4500ff4a884719c2cf9d5d20b1ef841ff036","tid":2188491,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f588376277849bfef013fa608025d20fee60d94","tid":2188491,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"睇個撚樣間學校應該已經剷撚咗成條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個職訓局系統根本就係同流合污"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"2019  校方 ： <span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\">原片已遺失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6q2jq4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6q2jq4o.jpg&h=483cb593&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c760d24e626538538c24092e890e81299784ce","tid":2188491,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"438f3a57693dd74f2a15fce057ea63f5cabfba13","tid":2188491,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"未能拍下彥霖脫鞋經過 係死角影唔到定係 下一秒無左對鞋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"睇  #7  <br />\n<br />\n全部都無故消失 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d02072df1d49b5ae7de98131254e213ba51c45","tid":2188491,"uid":354682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c679f496e54178dbf93e1cfebe14004c818b687a","tid":2188491,"uid":365109,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"你真係冇叫錯名"},{"pid":"f7cdbf2080034bd771e42c9b4495f24219bbf059","tid":2188491,"uid":365109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}